      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "燮理阴阳官极品，调和鼎鼐列三台。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00003",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "老夫，萧何。昨日在金殿之上，曾奉国太之命，言道三齐王韩信，统领天下兵将，兵权过重；倘若一起反心，汉室江山难保。特命老夫，将他诱入宫中，问他死罪，以防后患。我也曾命人邀请，还不见到来，想必来也。",
      "text_length": 96
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00004",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "操演将士出校场，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00005",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "韩信上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00006",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "午门外来了三齐王。撩袍端带朝廊上，只见萧何在朝堂。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00007",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "吓，萧丞相，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00008",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "三齐王。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00009",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同笑",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信",
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "吓，哈哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00010",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "丞相来得甚早？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00011",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "老夫已在此等候多时了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00012",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "今乃三、六、九日，操演之期，是俺在校场点卯，因此来迟，还望丞相海涵。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00013",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00014",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "丞相见招，不知有何国事议论？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00015",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "昨日太后，曾在金殿传旨，叫你我二人，今日一同进宫，有国事议论。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00016",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "但不知为了何事？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00017",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "这……老夫却也不知。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00018",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "如此你我一同进宫便了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00019",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "三齐王请！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00020",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "萧丞相请！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00021",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "龙国太因何故把旨传？倒叫我韩信难以详参。众诸侯并未曾兴兵造反，各番国又无有来犯边关。四方平靖河清海晏，五谷丰登共庆丰年。江河一统归炎汉，宣召我进宫去所为哪般？",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00022",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "三齐王休得要乱狐疑，细听老夫说端的：东荡西除功劳盖世，南征北剿谁敢对敌？到如今乐享太平世，满朝中文武臣可算第一。令日里宣你进宫去，定然是受赏把功题。",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00023",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "吓，丞相，今日这朝房之内，为何文武百官，一人不见，是何原故？",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00024",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "今日太后不曾临朝，在宫内宣召我等。想必他们无事，各自散去了。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00025",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "他们无事，各自散去了？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00026",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00027",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "吓，丞相，太后既然在宫那召见我等，为何这宫中太监、内侍，一个也不看见？",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00028",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "国太既在宫中，这内侍、太监等，想必均在宫中伺候一切。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00029",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "在宫中伺候一切？如此请。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00030",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "老夫告便。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00031",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "请便。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00032",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "萧何下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00033",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "你看这萧何老儿，年纪衰迈，言语颠倒，令人好笑。吓，这老儿转眼不见，他往哪里去了？想这皇宫内院，我并不曾走过；倘若错走，可就吃罪不起。嗳，想那萧何老儿，乃是当朝首相，既然可以穿宫入院，难道我韩信，身居王位。反倒不能在宫走走么？待我一人前去便了。",
      "text_length": 121
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00034",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "萧何虽然为首相，俺韩信官封三齐王。纵然进宫有谁敢挡？来在宫门看端详。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00035",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二宫女、吕后暗同上，吕后坐帐内。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00036",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "来此深宫，侍我看来。“未央宫”，“未央宫”。呵哈哈呀，来此已是未央宫！侍我在此。等侯萧何老儿便了。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00037",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "宫外何人讲话？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00038",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "三齐王韩信。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00039",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "你走近前来。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00040",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二宫女同撩帐。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00041",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "唗！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00042",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "韩信跪。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00043",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "胆大韩信，你私自闯进宫来，哀家正在沐浴之际！你私犯圣驾，该当何罪？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00044",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "启太后：今有萧何对臣言讲，国太传旨，宣我二人进宫，有国事议论。是以臣才敢前来。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00045",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "那萧何今在何处？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00046",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "今在宫外。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00047",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "宫娥。外面看来，可有萧何？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00048",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二宫女"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00049",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二宫女出帐，看。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00050",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二宫女"
      ],
      "text": "并无一人。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00051",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "唗！大胆韩信，你此番进宫，哀家倒也明白了：想是你看高皇晏驾，你要谋篡汉室社稷！既有谋反之心，又敢私犯圣驾。罪不容诛！宫娥们！",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00052",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二宫女"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00053",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "宣金瓜武士进宫！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00054",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二宫女"
      ],
      "text": "金瓜武士进宫。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00055",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四大铠、二太监同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00056",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "将韩信与我绑了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00057",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "好一大胆小韩信，私闯宫闱为何情！人来与我将他捆，定斩人头不容情！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00058",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人捆韩信。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00059",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "国太吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00060",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "国太且莫怒气生，细听为臣奏原因：萧何带臣把宫进，臣不该一人乱胡行。一时懵懂入宫禁，冒犯圣驾有罪名。望太后念臣功劳盛，念臣在朝秉忠心。将功折罪理应顺，望国太开放天地恩。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00061",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "你道你的功劳盛，未尝不存造反心。人来推出将他斩，斩却人头挂午门！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00062",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "想我韩信，统带天下将士，看哪一个敢来斩我？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00063",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈仓上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00064",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "我来斩你！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00065",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "吓，你是何人，胆敢出此大言，你叫什么名字？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00066",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "你问我么，我名叫陈仓。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00067",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "这“陈仓”二字，好像在哪里见过，怎么一时想它不起？呵哈是了，想当初癸未年间，我在淮阴避祸之时，失迷路途。遇一谯夫，名叫陈仓。那时蒙他指引路径，是我一时起了不良之心，恐怕他泄漏我的机关，是我将他杀死。莫非就是此人，转世投胎，前来索命么？待我向前来。吓陈仓，你今年多大年纪了？",
      "text_length": 136
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00068",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "我今年一十六岁了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00069",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，自癸未年算到如今，刚刚一十六载。苍天呐，天！这报应循环疏而不漏也！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00070",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "听说此女叫陈仓，倒叫韩信着了忙。他指引路途把命丧，如今投胎到朝堂。一十六年报冤枉，今日我韩信命必亡。事到头来想一想，自有天理暗昭彰。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00071",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "且住。想高皇命我统领天下将士，所有兵器上面，俱铸有“韩信”二字，只恐无刀可以杀我！",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00072",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "想这兵器之上，具有“韩信”字样，这便怎么处？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00073",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "启太后：宫中现有厨刀，料必无有“韩信”二字。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00074",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "好。快快取来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00075",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈仓下，持厨刀上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00076",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "果然无有“韩信”二宇。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00077",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "你叫他看来。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00078",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "是。韩信你看这把厨刀，可能杀你？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00079",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "唉，不好了！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00080",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "一见厨刀我心惊胆颤，想起了当年事一端：壬辰年遇相士把我的命算，他算我七十二岁命归天。怎奈我行事太短见，伤天害理难以保全。劝人生在世须要行善，莫学我韩信作恶多端：悔不该受高皇二十四拜，曾损我阳寿有八年；淮阴不该活埋母，折我青春寿八年；逼霸王在乌江把命丧，损我寿数又八年；背水阵害死兵丁十数万，又去了阳寿有八年；悔不该又把陈仓斩，折我青春寿八年。屈指从头仔细算，五八折去四十年。命中应活七十二，三十二岁染黄泉。只道苍天无明鉴，谁知报应有循环。末央宫今日身遭斩，方知道天网恢恢在眼前。",
      "text_length": 239
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00081",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "手执厨刀将他斩，管叫他一命丧黄泉！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00082",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "陈仓斩韩信，韩信下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00083",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "陈仓"
      ],
      "text": "首级献上！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00084",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "好一个刚强小陈仓，竟比男儿胆量强。钢刀一举命即丧，盖世功劳付汪洋。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00085",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "内侍，宣萧何进宫。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00086",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "内侍"
      ],
      "text": "国太有旨：宣萧何进宫。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00087",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "来也！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00088",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "萧何上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00089",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "忽听国太宣一声，来了开国保驾臣。想必是斩了小韩信，急忙进宫问分明。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00090",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "臣萧何见驾，国太千岁！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00091",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "卿家平身。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00092",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "千千岁！宣臣进宫，有何国事议论？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00093",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕后"
      ],
      "text": "韩信已经斩首，就命卿家将他尸首用棺木，成殓起来，埋葬在咸阳城外山麓之下，立一碑碣，以表他的功劳。领旨出宫。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00094",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吕后下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00095",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "领旨！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00096",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "萧何"
      ],
      "text": "在宫中领了国太命，背转身来自沉吟：韩信未央丧性命，可怜他汗马功劳化灰尘。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016005_e00097",
      "play_id": "01016005",
      "scene_id": "01016005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "萧何下。",
      "text_length": 4
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}